<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<h2>The Minor Program</h2>
<p>Mathematics is the study of abstract structures, space, change, and the interrelations of these concepts. It also is the language of the exact sciences.</p>
<h3>Minor Advisor</h3>
<p>For a current list of faculty and staff advisors; see <a href="https://www.math.ucdavis.edu/undergrad/advising/advisers/" target="_blank">Mathematics Department Advising</a> or contact <a href="mailto:studentservices@math.ucdavis.edu">Student Services</a>.</p>
]]>
</informationtext>
