<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Mathematics minor trains students in the mental habit of logical thinking and the tactics of problem-solving. The minor prepares students who are planning careers in industry, education, government, science, arts, humanities, engineering, or business.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
